nodes.text: The Coruscant sector was a sector located in the Core Worlds. Planets in the sector included Coruscant, Metellos and Utrost. The Coruscant sector was a subsector of the Corusca sector.

Under the New Order, it was called Imperial Sector and was part of Imperial Center Oversector. During the Galactic Civil War, the sector was governed by Moff Kadir. It was defended by the Coruscant Sector Fleet.
